data.title: Mary J. Blige
data.meta_description: Mary J. Blige is an American singer-songwriter, record producer, and occasional actress. She has won nine Grammy Awards and four American Music Awards, and has recorded eight multi-platinum albums. She is the only artist with Grammy Award wins in R&B, Rap, Gospel, and Pop.
data.text:
Mary J. Blige is an American singer-songwriter, record producer, and occasional actress. She has won nine Grammy Awards and four American Music Awards, and has recorded eight multi-platinum albums. She is the only artist with Grammy Award wins in R&B, Rap, Gospel, and Pop.
